{
  "texts": [
    "The validation of this strategy is hard without the execution of experimental analysis.",
    "Some works (Pang et al. 2021; Ren et al. 2021; Li et al. 2023a, b; Pang et al. 2021; Ren et al. 2021; Prakash et al. 2021; Rao et al. 2022b; An et al. 2022; Peng et al. 2021) use ablation analysis to demonstrate the influence of specific architectural elements on task accuracy.",
    "This analysis is very interesting since it supports, for example, simplifying the approach when we identify elements (e.g., A/B segment or the use of SEP special token) that are not significantly contributing to the learning process.",
    "In general, transformers suffer from a lack of benchmarks.",
    "Each work uses its own datasets, which are mostly not public."
  ]
}